OL,6,FChief Officer Brown told a Children,
OL,7,FEducation and Home Affairs Scrutiny
OL,8,FPanel of politicians: "We are not in
OL,9,Fthat situation at the moment.
OL,11,F"We do not have enough now to provide
OL,12,Ftwo sets of PPE that fit properly for
OL,13,Fall our firefighters.
