OL,3,CChief warns firefighters do not have
OL,4,Cenough kit to do jobs safely
OL,6,F"It's absolutely vital and you need
OL,7,Fmore than one piece of kit per person,
OL,8,Fbecause as soon as it's contaminated,
OL,9,Fit needs to go through a
OL,10,Fdecontamination process, but the
OL,11,Ffirefighters need to be decontaminated
OL,12,Fas well, before they can respond to
OL,13,Fthe next fire."
OL,15,FAccording to Dr Chris Edmond, an
OL,16,Foccupational physician, the
OL,17,Finfrastructure and knowledge in Jersey
OL,18,Fis 20 to 30 years behind the UK.
