OL,3,CChief warns firefighters do not have
OL,4,Cenough kit to do jobs safely
OL,6,FThe upcoming 2026 budget, which will
OL,7,Fbe debated in December, is set to
OL,8,Finclude a #413,000 cash boost for the
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Services, rising to
OL,10,F#1.3 million over the next three years.
OL,12,FThis will aim to strengthen the
OL,13,F"capacity and resilience" of the Fire
OL,14,Fand Rescue Service, and is "designed
OL,15,Fto ensure international standards are
OL,16,Fmet," following the concerns raised
OL,17,Fabout insufficient PPE.
